<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[الأفعال]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[المجرّد]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَعَلَ بالفتح، يَفْعُل بالضم<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[ب]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[فاتَ]</span>: الفَوْت: السَّبْق،<span class="c5"> يقال:</span> لا كلامَ على فائت،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span> وَلَوْ تَرى إِذْ فَزِعُوا فَلاا فَوْتَ <span class="c2">«١»</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[ح]</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[فاحَ]</span>: فاحت ريح الشيء: أي ثارت.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[خ]</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[فاخَ]</span>: فاخ الطِّيْبُ: مثل فاحَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[د]</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[فادَ]</span> فَوْدا: أي مات.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[ر]</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[فارَ]</span>: الفَوْر والفوران: الغَلَيان،<span class="c5"> يقال:</span> فارت القِدْر ونحوُها،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span> وَفاارَ التَّنُّورُ* <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">وفار الغضبُ:</span> إذا جاش،<span class="c5"> ويقال للغضبان:</span> فار فائرُه.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[ز]</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c4">[فاز]</span>: الفَوْز: النجاة.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">والفَوْز:</span> الظفر بالخير،<span class="c5"> يقال:</span> فاز به:<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>إذا ظفر به،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span> أَنَّهُمْ هُمُ الْفاائِزُونَ <span class="c2">«٣»</span> قرأ حمزة والكسائي بكسر الهمزة، والباقون بفتحها.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c4">[ظ]</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c4">[فاظ]</span> فَوْظا،<span class="c5"> بالظاء معجمةً:</span> إذا مات.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c4">[ق]</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c4">[فاق]</span>: فاق الرجلُ أصحابَه: إذا علاهم وصار فوقهم.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
